### 1. Get all products - SalesService
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/Products


### 2. Get customers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/Customers


### 3. Sales Orders with Items expand
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$expand=items


### 4. Sales Orders expand customer and items
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$expand=customer,items


### 5. Products filter stock less than 10
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=stock lt 10


### 6. Products order by price descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$orderby=price desc


### 7. Product Catalog report
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/ProductCatalog


### 8. Low Stock Alert report
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/LowStockAlert


### 9. Order Report
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/OrderReport


### 10. Purchase Orders with Items
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/PurchaseOrders?$expand=items


### 11. Deep Insert Sales Order
