}

### Day 17-Odata Query
### Products with price greater than 10000
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=price gt 10000

### Products with stock less than or equal to minimum stock
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=stock le minStock

### Products not equal to category 'Electronics'
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=category ne 'Electronics'

### GET price greater than equals to 50000
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=price ge 50000

### Check Department is active or not
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Suppliers?$filter=isActive eq true

### Date comparison - Orders created after June 1, 2026 
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$filter=orderDate gt 2026-06-01

### UUID comparison - Get product with specific ID
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=ID eq 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Null comparison - Get products with no category
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=category eq null

### Combining filters - Get products with price greater than 10000 and stock less than 50
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=price gt 10000 and stock lt 50

### Parantheses - Get products with price greater than 10000 and (stock less than 50 or category is 'Electronics')
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=price gt 10000 and (stock lt 50 or category eq 'Electronics')

### Parantheses - Get products with (price greater than 10000 and stock less than 50) or category is 'Electronics'
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=(price gt 10000 and stock lt 50) or category eq 'Electronics'

### // Orders placed in 2026
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders?$filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026

###  Orders placed in June 2026
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$filter=month(orderDate) eq 6

### $filter=year(orderDate) gt 2000
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders?$filter=year(orderDate) gt 2000

### $filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026 and month(orderDate) eq 6
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$filter=year(orderDate) eq 2026 and month(orderDate) eq 6

// Filter Expression
//"Show me all products that cost more than $50" → $filter=price gt 50
//"Find customers from India" → $filter=country eq 'India'
//"Get all active employees" → $filter=isActive eq true
// "Show orders placed after March 2026" → $filter=orderDate gt 2026-03-31
// "Find books with 'Lord' in the title" → $filter=contains(title, 'Lord')
// "Products with stock between 10 and 100" → $filter=stock ge 10 and stock le 100
// "Authors from UK or USA" → $filter=country eq 'UK' or country eq 'USA'
// "Orders that are NOT delivered and cost over $500" → $filter=not (status eq 'Delivered') and totalAmount gt 500

// Homework- Odata Query
### 1. All suppliers from Germany with their products
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=supplier/country_code eq 'DE'&$expand=supplier

### 2. Top 5 highest-value orders this month
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$filter=orderDate ge 2026-06-01 and orderDate lt 2026-07-01&$orderby=netAmount desc&$top=5

### 3. Products in Electronics category sorted by price
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=category/name eq 'Electronics'&$orderby=price asc&$expand=category

### 4. Page 2 of customers, 15 per page, sorted by name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Customers?$orderby=name asc&$top=15&$skip=15

### 5. Orders with status New and amount over 1000, with customer name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders?$filter=status eq 'New' and netAmount gt 1000&$expand=customer

### 1 GET Products from suppliers in India with supplier details
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=supplier/country_code eq 'IN'&$expand=supplier

### 4 Page 3 of customers, 2 per page, sorted by name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Customers?$orderby=name asc&$top=2&$skip=2

### 5 Orders with status Created and amount over 1000, with customer details
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/SalesOrders?$filter=status eq 'Created' and netAmount gt 1000&$expand=customer

