### Confirm a specific order
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders(ID='so111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111')/SalesService.confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Cancel a specific order
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders(ID='so111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111')/SalesService.cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer changed their mind"
}

### Ship an order
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/sales/SalesOrders(ID='so111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111')/SalesService.ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "TRK-2026-ABC123",
  "carrier": "FedEx"
}